728359f-b.text:
(1)
429 Arthur Kill Road, north side, at the head of Giffords Lane, showing the Mary B. Ferentes house (1907). It belonged earlier to Mrs. Rizpah Boehm (1898). The dates refer to maps upon which the names of the owners appear. The view is north on Giffords Lane.
December 31, 1911
By Wam. T. Davis
Throuugh 7. L. Sperr
(2)
A closer view of the house.
June 13, 1927
P. L. Sperr
